BRIDGE.pcMessage: Use Bridge category only for a named road bridge with local or navigational significance.

FIRE_DEPARTMENT.pcMessage: Only Fire Stations providing first response to nearby emergencies should use this category.

HOSPITAL_MEDICAL_CARE.pcMessage: Only Hospitals,Emergency Rooms,and Urgent Medical Care places should use this category. Other medical offices should use the Office category.

STADIUM_ARENA.pcMessage: If this is a small/local ballfield or arena,consider using the \"Sports Court\" category and making it a point place.

SEA_LAKE_POOL.pcMessage: Use the Sea/Lake/Pool category only if water is visually obvious to drivers on nearby roads. Do not remap features already present in the built-in Waze water layer unless that layer is incomplete or inaccurate.

RIVER_STREAM.pcMessage: Use the River/Stream category only if water is visually obvious to drivers on nearby roads. Do not remap features already present in the built-in Waze water layer unless that layer is incomplete or inaccurate.

EMERGENCY_SHELTER.pcMessage: Emergency Shelter type should only be used for places that should appear as crisis centers on the app. Please consult your regional managers for the appropriate use of this category.
